transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thanks for calling Viagra, Quinn speaking. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yeah, how are you doing? I was online trying to figure out how to cancel my account,

Speaker 1: and it doesn't give an option on the website to cancel.

Speaker 2: There is an option on there.

Speaker 1: I'm sorry?

Speaker 2: No, but we can help you out. There's an option on there, but we can help you out with that.

Speaker 1: What's going on with the Viagra? Why is it that you don't want it anymore?

Speaker 2: Medical reasons, I can't use it.

Speaker 1: Oh, okay. Well, let's see, you kind of just got this.

Speaker 2: Did some things change? Because, you know, this was prescribed by a doctor.

Speaker 1: It's been three months.

Speaker 2: When I went to my primary care physician, I'm having an issue with my heart.

Speaker 1: She said do not take Viagra or any other ED medication anymore.

Speaker 2: Okay, well, I know sometimes you guys do get cleared to pick back up with this type of stuff down the line.

Speaker 1: When that is the case, we can always just put this on hold for you for like a half a year,

Speaker 2: give you some time to figure things out.

Speaker 1: No, I just need to cancel it, man.

Speaker 2: All right, we'll cancel you out.

Speaker 1: Have a good day, sir.

Speaker 2: Pardon me, can you send me an e-mail verification that it's canceled, please?

Speaker 1: No, we don't send any e-mail verifications, but I can confirm that everything was just canceled for you.

Speaker 2: Okay, and then how about directing me on the website to where the cancellation request would be?

Speaker 1: You can sign into your website, and you can see under your prescriptions that everything says you are,

Speaker 2: that there is no more prescription there.

Speaker 1: It says you are not currently on auto-ship, and everything hasn't stopped.

Speaker 2: Okay, when I go into my prescriptions, there's no way.

Speaker 1: Yeah, I'm in my prescriptions right now.

Speaker 2: It doesn't give an option to stop it.

Speaker 1: That's because everything has stopped.

Speaker 2: If you go to the last option on the bottom right, you will see that it says you are not currently on anything.

Speaker 1: That's because everything has been stopped.

Speaker 2: Oh, down at the bottom under auto-ship.

Speaker 1: Yes, sir.

Speaker 2: It says you are not currently on auto-ship.

Speaker 1: Anything else that you need.

Speaker 2: That's all I needed, buddy.

Speaker 1: All right, you have a good day.
